{"tid":1965744,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"好心無好報 遇見飛機師","createTime":"2020-04-09T16:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T03:00:54.000Z","uid":90800,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a14acd1cd3f43c31c234892538d2a358a1c45b","tid":1965744,"uid":90800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"尋日本身約左下面條友 (<span style=\"color: red;\">其中一個</span>) 今晚1900油麻地 交收Switch<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但手機台有巴打話壞左電話, 而且又失業, 所以我就約1815九龍灣 $100賣部電話俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我遲左收工, 所以我最後要1835先完成交收<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好肯定唔夠時間坐巴士, 但無理由又遲到, 只好焗坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於我早上已經同飛機師夾好到達時間, 所以我就18:56到左油麻地先同佢講到左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知飛機師已經係跑道滑行緊, Cleared All History<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rhs6oTz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhs6oTz.jpg&h=66e2a25f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n當我存心希望機師只係錯手, 會番轉頭的時侯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個鐘已經係19:03, 已讀不回, 肯定起飛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點黎啦</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當我睇下佢個Profile既時侯竟然見到以下相片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qCRyOnU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqCRyOnU.jpg&h=916048d2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而且我竟然知道相中左一個個人的資料</span></strong></span><br />\n但因為佢唔係叫阿HIM, 所以我暫時覺得唔關佢事, 唔講佢D資料出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我細心D睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相中D人除曬口罩影相, 即係張相都係呢3個月內影, 未必係假相, 真實性較高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WGNYZzH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWGNYZzH.jpg&h=3ce443ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我再細心D睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xSNexVh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxSNexVh.jpg&h=27c15a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢個id叫 wil558<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我大膽小小推測, wil 可以係Wilson / William / Will / Wilfred 甚至 真係叫 Wil<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即係呢4個人裡面, 邊個個名叫阿謙 (HIM) 或者 Wil英文開頭都有機會係飛機師</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下內容係致親愛的飛機師:<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係好大件事, 同SWITCH全套唔算好重, 但我好希望你可以正正式式道個歉, 因為你唔要可以係中午同我再Confirm的時候講, 或者 你都可以係你有決定一刻同我講, 因為我又唔會迫你買, 只要你講一聲就可以好完美解決個問題. 我相信你已經30歲有多了, 希望你可以有D承擔.<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母,<br />\nSwitch賣家上"},{"pid":"c0defe59d4906ccec21f62d6dc7cc65e80719a10","tid":1965744,"uid":182334,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"唔買講聲有幾難?"},{"pid":"368ab2ad3a403c6ddbcc36a173d6642255a816ae","tid":1965744,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"Sorry呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cfb37525652622ae92cb74893591b475779a93","tid":1965744,"uid":103936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"368ab2ad3a403c6ddbcc36a173d6642255a816ae","tid":1965744,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"reply